\par }\pard \ltrpar\qj \fi-461\li461\ri0\sa240\widctlpar\wrapdefault\aspalpha\aspnum\faauto\adjustright\rin0\lin461\itap0\pararsid16388725 {\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15018283\charrsid12525446 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15018283\charrsid12525446 Can you remember }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
what happened when your father was out of work, how did you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 manage}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We
ll I'll tell you how - how we managed, it was a very long strike. And - they had soup kitchens at some of the - some of the schools, one school had it one day and another had it another day and there was a place pulled down over there, they had it once ab
out four in week. You - you either got some - jam and bread and corned beef and of course a cup of a tea and some - some used to make soup and you'd take a - a jug and get some soup.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your mother work before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. She worked before - that's at another that's pulled down up there. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 She worked - I can just remember, oh well, how old would I be - I working at - I wouldn't above six and I took her dinner up there, and father then were 'complaining with rheumatic and he 
used to be cooking the din - the meals here and she worked up there getting a bit of money I suppose, keep us.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did she do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 It was a cotton mill. That -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She worked in the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. In the card room.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That was hard work in the card room wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah well she worked there. I can just remember taking the dinners there, he used to get the dinner ready.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Your dad used to look after you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye while he - while he - he - while he were - while they were on strike and same while he were '}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 complaining}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  with this - rheumatics.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did she ever work while your father was working?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Never. No, no very few - very few women worked then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This house where you lived the longest, {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}Market Street
{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}, how many rooms did you have?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Two upstairs and two down.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have relatives or anyone living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, not - not until - I - I Had an old sister. But my - father were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  twice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Your mother died when you were how old?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She was thirty-seven when she was - died. She were thirty-seven, so that'll leave me about six year old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And then your father }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He - he - aye, he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 my mother. And the other woman of course I wouldn't know you know. And there was a girl - well, she'd be - four or five years older than me. And she used to look after us, I can - I can remember very little about her only when she got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You don't remember whether she helped a lot - dress you and undress you and things like that?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I - no, well probably the - I'd be dressing myself you know. And the other - well probably the youngest may have wa
nted - I can't remember doing so much that way but they used to bake.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She used to bake all her own bread did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Make - bake bread.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did she make jam and pickles?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, she didn't make jam but she used to - used to make potato pies and that like of that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember what you had for meals in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - we were never short of grub. No. No. We were - I - I'd only the clothes I sat up in and stockings you know but I w
ere - I never were short of grub.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How many times a week would you have meat do you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Meat? Probably twice a week but we'd always porridge of a morning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Always porridge for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Porridge and milk.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have anything special on Sunday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
We used to have - used to get - get beef for Saturday and Sunday. Father used to go up on Farnworth Market and buy shin beef. I used to love it you know them big lumps of -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did she make from it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh - he used to do the cooking of a weekend you know, did me - me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well he - whether he helped me mother or not I don't know. Only he used to have them big lumps of - steak and pro
bably a rabbit or - rabbit were worth about - about ninepence then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You never poached rabbit or bought any from poachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Poached rabbits. Yes. And when they get - when they get a poached rabbit }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 there's}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  as much difference as - well, these you get in shops are nothing like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And they used to have poachers round here you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Tell me about them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I - I used to go in a pub where they used to go up - up - up ther
e to the side of canal and they used to go occasionally and you could get one for - get a couple for about eighteenpence.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why were they always better?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh they were - they were different - different taste. I - I bought one the other week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Not a poached one surely?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No. I bought one the other week just to get the taste of rabbit back again and - practically it went in fire. No, they're no good at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But just the family lived at your house when you lived at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}
}Market Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The - just - ayes, just the family and - with this girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you manage to sleep with only having two bedrooms?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - you see, they were - the girl slept in a bed by herself and the two l
ads, two younger brothers slept together and father and me slept together you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where did your mother sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh she was dead at then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Before she died where would she sleep?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh but she were but s
mall then you know and - and we were but small and she lived there then. I can remember her quite well.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 After your mother died who brought you up - this step-sister?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, yes, and father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They brought you up together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So she more or less took over the household did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your sister ever have any help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She didn't. I never - I never knew anybody - to come and give us a lift but mind y
ou, I'll just tell thee something about that bread making. We had somebody lived next door but one and - they used shop bread and she used to bake beside. But it baking used to be baked in pots. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 In pots like loaf tins and - it used to be right good 'til this lady boiled a loaf next door and when she used to bring her loaf back the three of us used to yell. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Couldn't take it. There wasn't - no, there was that much difference between - between her baking and the woman's baking. You'll hardly believe that but it were true. Aye, and it was so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your sister help mend or make the family's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well, no - I tell you we only used to have one suits. One suit and clogs.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your father mend the clogs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, we - he - the - a cloggers shop - oh we used to get the clogs ironed there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your sister do all the washing herself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She used to do the washing and - father used to help you know, she wasn't too old. And there were another thing I - I 
suppose I'd better tell you. At the end of the road was an old girl with a shop. This girl got going there and there was always lot of lads in. And amongst the lot of them they got her pregnant. You see. And I remember it nearly - it nearly got me - it ne
arly got me down old as I were and I couldn't do - I wouldn't be above twelve years old. And she had this youngster. And it led - it lived about - twelve or eighteen months.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She still stayed at home with you though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They would do nothing else, yes, she stayed at home and - after that she got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 and then her husband come living with us. And she had a youngster with him. I only went to the funeral the - she was a Roman Catholic. And you know they don't get Roman Catholic places often when you're a Protestant. And they buried her -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She turned Roman Catholic for him did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you Roman Catholic?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. No, I'm a Protestant. She - she }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  a - a fellow and he - he were a Roman
 Catholic, they buried her just about a - a month since. And she never would come down very much. 'Cos of another - another - another aunt there and she'd had - she had her living with her and they didn't get on together. See, you'd come and see me occasi
onally and then she got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  she never come.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So did she do all the housework?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did your father help with then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh well he - he used to help with the baking. And he used to cook the meat at weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did he help wash or undress you and things like that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - oh aye, he'd do things like that. He - but he - he - he were very good that way were me father.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did he read to you at all or tell you stories?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, he - he used to tell us tales, he - and - he was a very good runner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He took part in sport then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well - he were working 'til - at that time before he went in he were working at - the - paper mill. And by the way, better not put this in, in there - on -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember the hours that he worked at the paper mill? Do you remember anything about it - the pay or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I couldn't remember his pay, I know what I had, I had two and fivepence ha'penny a week when I worked there. Half time.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You started at the paper mill did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And you worked half time did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I worked half time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Tell me about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When I got full time I - I went to this pit loading coal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you get your first job at the paper mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did I get it? I went and asked for it at the - at the office.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You said you got two and five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Two and fivepence ha'penny.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I - I was - I was catching the paper as it come off the reels as it were cut, making in - and then - they piled it on a wagon and take it off.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What was it used for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They - they - they only used - made tissue then and biro - biro paper.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember how many hours you worked?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. I got up at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 17}}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 30}}}half past five{\*\xmlclose} and I started at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 18}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}
{\xmlattrvalue 0}}}six o'clock{\*\xmlclose} and I worked 'til twelve.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 At night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 At what?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh, dinner time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, I only did half a day you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Then you went to school in the afternoon?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't so much - don't know so much about the afternoons. I went school at afternoon you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you work Saturday or Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Worked Saturday but not Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Just half a day Saturday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you get holidays with pay in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Hm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you feel that it was a fair wage that they paid you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - I never thought nothing about it. I remember spending - the odd halfpenny coming home and I'm standing}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 at shop and - father kicked up a row. He didn't hit me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Because you took a ha'penny out of your wages?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Aye, of me - there were another halfpenny for what they took it for - some purpose, I don't know why. It should have been two and six but they took it - halfpenny out for accident benefit or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have to give all the money to your dad or did you get spends?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I can't remember giving me penny, might have given me a penny or tuppence but not much more.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you like the job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I liked all right. I liked it, I liked it. The - the - load
ing the boats too. That were a good job, I'd nine bob a week for that job when I went on the boats.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did your employer treat you in the paper mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh well - we were all right at paper mill, they were - there were no - there were no supervision same as there is now.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you like the people you worked with too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, I liked - yes, of course I liked the people I worked with.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 After that you went to loading boats?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Loading boats. As was - as was going to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}
Manchester{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. With - with coal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How old would you be then - this was when you started in the pit wasn't it? What age did you start work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - probably when I - what would I be - I'd be full time then I'd be fourteen or fifteen. Hardly full might be.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This is when you went loading boats you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 went}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  into mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you were loading boats you got nine shillings a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Nine bob a week, it were good pay that them days you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 like}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh I liked it, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What about the people you worked with there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well they were all right.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And the bosses?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, the - I didn't - coming back again - aye, they were pretty decent.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you work Saturdays there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Any holidays with pay?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. We hadn't holidays with pay then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember the hours you worked in this full time job? Six in the morning 'til five?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But you didn't work Sundays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, no Sunday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you think nine shillings was a fair wage?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well it were then, eighteen bob - eighteen bob were a - were a labourer's wage then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So nine shillings as boys was good wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh it - it were good.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Then you went on to the mill didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Then I come - from there I came to mill here. Started here. Little piecing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What's that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I - there's little piecer, side piecer and minder. And on t' weft there were little piecer, side piecer - little piecer, coarse piecer and side piecer and spinner. Then - when I - when I came to mill. And we started at s
ix o'clock at morning, half an hour for breakfast. And then, you'd an hour for dinner and then you worked 'til half past five.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How much pay did you get then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I think it were - it were either ten and six or eleven and six, I went little piecing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So it was more than loading coal?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. And - and then you was clean, you wasn't black you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you like this job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I liked this job.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were conditions good in the mill in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well, you see, you never thought about 'em, I mean, if just depend who you work for. If the - if the spinner was a decent fellow you were all right and if he were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 cranky}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and couldn't do his job you went through it too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 In what way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I mean, there used to be some narkey fellows and they - and they'd never let you have a minute.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 If you stopped they'd shout at you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well never would shout but - the - the bulk of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 fellows}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  were - were good - were good - what I call good spinners.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You gradually worked yourself up to be a spinner?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
You worked - you worked yourself up from little piecing to - if you went in weft you could get cross piecing and from cross piecing you got side piecing and then the next job was spinning.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You stayed a spinner all your life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I stayed a spinner all me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you like it? Would you have liked to have done something else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Hm. Aye. I - no, wel
l you see - without me mother I practically tied to me dad. You see. I can tell you this about when the - about when the Boer war were going - there were six on us went to list and - and - me and another fellow had a bit of money and we - I'd just started
 
drinking then, having - pints. So - we got to this fellow and we - he looked at us and measured 'em up and one thing and another and - he said, he said, I', sorry, he said, out of the lot of you only, there's only him I'll take. That were me. And he were 
d
runk were this recruiting sergeant. They used to give you a shilling and when you got that shilling you were done for you know. So - he says, have you got a moth - a good mother and father, this fellow says to me surprisingly. I said, I've no mother, I sa
id, but I've a good father. He says, have you? I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15018283\charrsid12525446 say,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 aye. Have you any - what was - I said, I've two brothers. He says, he says, go back, and, he said, if you come again, he said, you'll not get off so easily, so I -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He sent you away?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
The recruiting sergeant - he felt sorry for me. And he - he - and he wouldn't have any of the other - the other fell - the other five so I come back again.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your dad know you'd been?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I never told him. Well - if - if he'd took one of the others I should have been done for Boer war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You liked working in the mill did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I liked working in the mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Can you tell me about conditions there when you were young?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - as it happens this mill here -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Which mill is that - what's the name of it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The - that one - it's standing now - empty. Curtis's is using it now for a store place. But -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 It was Woodbank did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Woodband spinning mill - it still has it on. Oh I liked working in the mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And conditions were good were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
They were good - they were good and they were one - it were one of best paid - wages there were, they were getting five or six quid a week then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did the bosses treat you, before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
The bosses were all right only they used to be - on the top of you, they used to walk through you know. They weren't bad bosses. And - and this place here was one of be
st spinning places in - in - in Lancashire and they spun - they spun a hundred and twelves and hundred and twenty-two spin cup and you never changed for years. All the mills were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 changing}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  all the different counts but this mill - they could spin - they coul
d spin it out of a - a - oh I think they hadn't a crop of cotton on the other - the other places on account of it being between the Mersey - in between the river and the canal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Because there was more moisture in it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you in a trade union in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh I were in trade union them days.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you take any part in its activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Well - as a matter of fact I used go there pretty frequently as a - as a delegate from the mill here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you feel that employers that workers had the same interest in those days or did you think they had different interests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - we - we'd - the people that - that run the mill there - their names - they were {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Manchester{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} p
eople - Mr Wood. And they built this new mill here, and they built the old one. And they built that Prestaley school there for the - for the workers. I always liked - I always liked this Mr Wood and - and his sons and daughters.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was it for the children of the workers that he built the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You'd be too old to go to it wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I - I didn't - I used go Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you feel that there was a division of interest between the workers themselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, they were very good work were - were Woods the people int' village. Especially Mrs Wood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Tell me about it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - the reason I know there were a fellow and he - he were a bricklayer and he were 
very tall, he were about six foot seven. They couldn't do his job. Well I used to - go and sit with this fellow when he came down - when he come down int' village, living int' village and Mrs Wood come in one day and I'm sitting with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 this}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  fellow. He says, 
you've no need to go out Mr Fox. I said, no. When I were going out I see'd him grab a shawl and put it round him and she - they'd be giving him money. And I - I didn't go and see him any more. I could see the game you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What do you think he was doing - do you think he was sponging?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I bet you he was a sponger, he used to sponge on me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And she was very soft heated was she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah well was very good was Mrs Wood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But do you think the workers themselves all had the same interest?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, I can say - see what - I can see the feeling for - about unrest between the workers and the - and the management.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you find any?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Very little, very little there. And I worked at another mill when this shut down at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
Bolton{\*\xmlclose} and there wasn't any unrest there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They all liked the bosses did they - did you think there was a big division between trained craftsmen and the people who weren't trained?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I mean these - these people working here on the big long }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 mules,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  they - they called - what is it - weavers got}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446  a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  good wage, I should imagine so but spinners were - were - well away on the top of the average you know, they were above - they were - they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8219239\charrsid12525446 were}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  above the fitters and that, they were getting more money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What about the people you were telling me on the mules?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh the mules. The mule spinners I'm talking about now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You thought that a craftsman was better off than a workman?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
He - he wasn't - he - he'd have about - he'd be getting fifty-bob a week as a mechanic he was doing well. They getting seven or eight quid a week there you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Before 1918 do you think there was a big difference between a craftsman and someone who hadn't a trade?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, I shouldn't say there were. Only they - this about the tradesman he used to - he could always work overtime, he could build his wage up you know but then - there no - no overtime - no overtime with the 
mule spinners. The - on these big mules, the little mules you know were - the old mules were - they were different people - different people altogether, they all - they all wanted to get in there and another thing while that were going you know - you'd ge
t - twenty-seven year old before you got mule spinning. Aye, you see, can - can -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you bound apprentice?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. Can't you see it, there were five men coming up to - five people coming up for - one spinner. And then - when the time 
got these big mules you could get on - get spinning at twenty-four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But 'til then it took until you were twenty-seven because you'd to workup?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. And the spinner at one while he used to get the - the wage for the whole wheelgate,
 what they call the wheelgate, and he used to pay these piecers. P}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
id what their weekly wage were - eighteen bob - eighteen bob and twelve bob and - and ten bob. That - in - in - in that respects you see he - he was the - he were employing them people. I'l
l never forget the - bringing the wages, bringing piecers wages up separate. And I know I tell 'em - I told 'em at shop meeting, I says, bang goes the spinners superiority. They weren't his men then, they belonged to the same - the - management you see. A
ye, aye, the - the - where the spinner were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 their}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 boss then but he wasn't so much the boss when it - when they - when they begun paid separately.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Until }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 then}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  he could do more or less what he liked with you?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Aye. I said, his - his superiority went then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you were working full time do you think it changed your attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - I'll tell you this, when they started - when they knocked Saturday off it - it - that a big relief.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You didn't like Saturday work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well I - I mean you never thought nothing about it used to but when - of about hollering to get out at twelve but when they knocked it off of course it passed away you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Once you left school and were working did you feel differently about life?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't - it was a pretty hard slog, you hadn't time to think about anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Tell me about your home life as a child, your father used to help with all the jobs about the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have jobs to do at home with having no mother?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
There - there - there were nothing I could do were there. Well I mean, there - there were this - this - sister, our sister or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 there}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  were me dad. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 He did}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  nothing only play }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 with }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You didn't do anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh no, I - that was - that's where I missed me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you not help the younger children in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well they got in bother I used to have to go out and fight for them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you expected to go to bed at a certain time on schooldays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah I - I would be probably - probably bed be - be {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname 
Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 10}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}}ten o'clock{\*\xmlclose}. Ah it were late then. But - we used to be ready for - going when it get eight - going seven or eight you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What would you do until ten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh we - playing at football or - messing about with t'other lads.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And then you were called in and you went to bed about ten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah. Ten probably, we were always in bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Who put you to bed with having no mother until you were old enough to put yourself to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We put ourselves to bed, we'd no trouble that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Who put you to bed when you were very tiny?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah - well - that were when I had me mother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Your mother put you to bed then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Can you tell me what room you bathed in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We used to have - and - and one - we generally trotted off to baths at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 Farnsworth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 .
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How many times a week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Once. Weekend. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When did you change your clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I should think we'd change them every week. The shirts and - and - and flannel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where did the family have their meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We had it in't house - had it in t' house - all round the table.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 In the front room?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, yes, yes, all had a table then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where did your sister cook?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 On the open fire, there wasn't fires like these you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She had a range did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, we had the oven you know. And the - we had the - the boiler. The heater with the fire and tap at front you know.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What time did you have breakfast as a family and who was there? Your dad would be off to work first wouldn't he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - I - I don't know who we - how we get it when were going to school, used to have it before we went school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You don't remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Not - not much about that. It used to be porridge I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Never anything else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - at weekend - ah, used to get eggs. Eggs would }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 
only a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  penny each - penny a piece then you know and we'd milk. Milk, it was penny a gill of milk were.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you usually have for your tea meal? You said you'd have meat some days and always a stew at weekend?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah well we used to - used to have a - a potato pie you know at least once a week.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid12525446  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 And}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 - and - and with a suet crust on you know. Oh aye. Used to like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You don't remember your tea meals - what you had for tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, used to get boiled ham - boiled ham or some corned beef.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your father grown your own vegetables?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. I used to grown them here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember ever having tinned vegetables or fruit or tinned meat?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, and I - nothing only tinned salmon. And used to get the tinned pineapples. With it being three lads you know used to have these chunks and - used to get one of them big t
ins and - we always tricks on - on - on the middle one, the younger brother and me. And - he used to have it - when it used to be }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 on t}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ' shelf in kitchen, used to get him one out you know, or - or two as a matter of fact, they were going out so we put - cut
 the potato up and stuck in him and waited on him - on him going - aye. Aye, we used to play tricks on him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was your father an easy person to talk to and could you share your worries with him?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Father? Oh well he was - he' he'd tal
k, he were all right. And he weren't - and he didn't go to school so much. And yet he could - he could read but I don't think he could write. But he could read.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was he affectionate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, he were good dad. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He was a nice chap, very good to you and kind?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you allowed to talk during meals or not?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Would I what? Oh yes, we used talk - used talk to me - talk to me dad and used to ask him things and - there were no - th
ere were no - no bother that way, there were no discipline in the house that way. Only we didn't do what we - we didn't do what we wanted you know, we -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He used to punish you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He only hit me once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What was that for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I done - had another uncle down. And - he - both of them were running at time and - I chucked it. And I were telling me uncle about it and said to him I didn't want run you know so I - they'd both been out - the other one had come from up - up No
rth somewhere and he hadn't seen him for forty year, so you can guess what they were like, they had a pint or two and they dug in and when I told him something about this running - whack. That were the only time he ever hit me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you feel about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I told him, I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 said}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 , you'll not hit me no more, I said, I'm off lifting tomorrow. Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This was when you went to enlist?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. Not then, that were another time, I were older then. I said, you'll not hit me no m
ore, to him. Anyway - this - this - his brother - father's brother were waiting at the bridge when I come out of factory. Come here, he says, he says, let's go and have a gill. I went and he said, he said, they're not - you're not going to leave your dad 
are you. I said, I don't know. He says, don't. So it passed off that way and that were all there were to it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How old would you be then when he hit you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh - oh I'd be spinning then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You'd be in your teens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. I were twenty-eight. I know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Suppose you were at the table and there was something you wanted could you ask for it or did you have to wait until it was offered to you?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, oh yes - ah, yes, we used to - we used to - I tell 
you we always had some good grub. There were one thing he looked after, me dad looked after, he looked see what good - good meat.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Could you have what you wanted or did you have to have what you were given?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I - me and my br
other, youngest brother used to get up and we used to count the eggs and if there were a dozen we usually had one apiece for me dad and t'other brother and we used to eat that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Had you always got to clean your plate?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - was never nothing left there, we were never short of anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Could you ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh we used to eat it 'til it were done. And then -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Suppose you left something on your plate, what happened?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well he - he - I don't suppose there were anything ever left. And we'd sufficient.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you taught to hold your knife and fork in a certain way and did you have your own place at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We had - we had a knife and fork.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have your own place at the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I always used to sit at the same place at table and all - under the lamp you know we had lamps then in - no gas.;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Could you bring a book or toys to the table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I didn't - not so often as it were - oh no, we ready for it - we'd no - no books.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You weren't allowed to bring books?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Could you leave the table when you wanted?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh leave the table when they wanted, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And you all sat at the table for the meal?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We all sat, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Who served the meal with your mother being dead?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Either me dad or you'd get your own out of the dish.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You'd all serve yourselves?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Uh-huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You weren't served in any special order then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, no. No. Only when it used to be rabbit I know - I know there's only two back legs on a rabbit - I used to get one, me dad used to have the rest and t'other used - they used to sort the rest - they used to do that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did your father bring you up to behave towards your brothers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I never had any bother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Suppose somebody outside hit you did he tell you to hit back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't - he didn't - he - I know - I don't know what we were but he didn't need. Did it myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What kind of a person do you think your father hoped you'd grow up to be, what did he think was right and wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well you see - when I get - when I gets s
pinning it were - it - I could - spinners then at them big mules were the aristocrats of labour. They're getting - they're getting good money.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you think he wanted you to be a spinner?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't - I don't think he - he - he bothered - he - he - when I got spinning you see, he - he - he give over working.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Because of we'd - we'd money enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Would your wage keep you and the family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 'Course it would, oh dam - dammit a - a pound y
ou could have fend a table with a - with grub then, a pound - a pound to spend a pound a week at grocers I mean -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did your father do at home all day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He looked after t'house.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He became the woman of the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well really yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That's unusual isn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Mm. Oh he good chap, my dad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did he think was important in life, what did he teach you was right and what did he teach you was wrong?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well you see, you
 - what happens, after we'd had he used - put his boots on he used to go bowling - he were a rattling bowler too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He took part in sport did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did he bet or go to races?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Not so much. He - not - he betted but not much. Shillings. He never - never - never over-reached that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You said after you'd had your tea he used to go bowling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Go along }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}bowling}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  green{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} over belonging to that pub at t'other side of the bridge there, it's not in use now. Used to go bowling there.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What was right and what was wrong according to your dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh he - he - he - he wouldn't - he wouldn't have - he wouldn't allow us do anything you know, and - or swear or anything like that. No, no. He - probably - but he never had any trouble with us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You were all good boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I suppose so.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When grown ups were talking were you allowed to join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Talk to him? When he used to go - used to pull all't lads in. You know, he'd played dominoes and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You had a lot of visitors did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, used to have lads come in with there being no woman there you could come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever go visiting with your dad?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, I used to - I used to go - go {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Bolton{\*\xmlclose} with him.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Who did you visit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Didn't visit none, we used to go and watch - Wanderers or - if there were any sports on at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
place}}Bolton{\*\xmlclose} he'd go there with being a runner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You never went visiting friends or relatives at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. No, they - they used to come home visit us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember going away for Bank Holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah - we used to go to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Blackpool{\*\xmlclose}. {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}
}Blackpool{\*\xmlclose} when he was - everybody went {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Blackpool{\*\xmlclose} then, down at - down at village more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have a regular holiday - did you go away for a holiday?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, do a - do a week at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Blackpool{\*\xmlclose}
. You could do a week for about a couple of quid then you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you do when you got there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Messed about from one pub to another.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You wouldn't do that as a boy would you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well, no, I'm talking when I were older as I couldn't get there as a boy.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You never went holidays as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, no, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you never go away on Bank Holidays as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, no, not then. This were when -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 After you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, before I were wedded - before I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 . Used go for
 a weekend. 'Cos I'd money then you know, I were rolling in money. I - I'll tell you some - I had a suit of clothes then believe me, a brown suit and I believe I paid four quid for it or something about like that - that were extraneous in them days - I wa
s up }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 Farnsworth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 one day with this suit on and me clogs and a fellow come and touched me. He says, excuse me, he says, would you mind telling me where you had that suit from? }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 I stared at him. }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I said, yes, I said, I got it from Morley and Burns. And when he w
ere going away he said, don't you think, he said, don't you think you'd have looked better he said, if you'd have had your boots on to it. That suit were that good. And I wore it and wore it and wore it and I gave it to a fellow over here when I come - wh
en I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 . And he took it pawn shop and I must have had it years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember the pawn shops?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I remember the pawn shops.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Which school did you go to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh I went to one as is pulled down at t'other side of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 
\endash }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 t\rquote other}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  side of bridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What type of school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 It was a Wesleyan school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 It was a church school was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, Wesleyan school - yes, a church school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How old were you when you first started?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Eeh, what were we, I'd be four else five. And I paid. Fourpence a week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How old were you when you left?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh - I - I left when I'd be - I think I told you I were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 
working}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  at ten. Half time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What time did you start school and what time did you finish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well we - somewhat similar time to the - nine - nine 'til dinner time and then we }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 went at}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  half past one 'til four o'clock.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Then you started doing half time didn't you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What age would that be?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well it were ten then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you started doing half time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Half time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You didn't do half time school and half time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. I went to mill at this time at half past - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour
}{\xmlattrvalue 17}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 30}}}half past five{\*\xmlclose} or - or - five or {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 18}}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}}six o'clock{\*\xmlclose} 'til dinner time and then after dinner I went school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was it girls and boys mixed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you like your teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I got on very well with the - with the teachers better than the headmaster.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why didn't you like him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well - he - he - he were once asking a lad - we were stood round the blackboard - what a petticoat were. And the lad didn't understand and neithe
r did I. But he started kneeing and bumping into him - mind you - I wasn't working then so I must have been eight or nine year old. I just getting ready for run and give him a good kick when he were at this job 'til he stopped it. So I stopped too.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did they punish you a lot?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No. He - he did used - he did used to at the top school. Be having you up for idle at - at top school where he came from, another Wesleyan school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You went to two schools did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I'
m talking about the schoolmaster now. Oh well he'd come down from the top job to this bottom one at school here he - he - ceremoniously broke the sticks up and he wouldn't use the cane. But he used to use his knee. He did do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember what the things were that you were punished for at school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Generally fighting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You were always fighting were you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, not so often.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did they punish the girls as well as the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I never - I - I never remember them punishing the girls.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you think of school, did you like it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I can't say I did - only - only - with - with certain teachers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Would you have stayed on longer if you could have done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well it would have paid me. I've always - I've always regretted it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you go on to any other school afterwards, part time education, night school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. That were - that were where we were lacking. And then when you - when you - you're working and getting up at 
{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 18}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 30}}}half past six{\*\xmlclose} you - you haven't much patience for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where did you have your dinner when you were at school? Did you come home for it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh, I come home to me dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was it near to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, just short - just across the road.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You'd go on your own then wouldn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, oh yes, I would go on me own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your dad take an interest in your school, did he ever go to school or see the teachers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, no, wouldn't bother generally don't bother with us that way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were the children all form the same kind of home as you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Practically.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever find that teachers had pets, they singled them out for anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, I - I can't say as there was any - any pets in the school, only the - school - master used to be a bit particular to one - woman teacher. I can remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But you don't remember him making an exception to any children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have gangs in the school at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I - no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever remember children being left out of things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I can remember one thing. There were a girl lived at this si
de of bridge here and she'd a very poor home. And he had a second wife had this fellow. And this girl - they were - this - this kids were dragged up. I knew that - four of the lads. And one day she pinched somebody's - somebody's meat, I don't know - I do
n
't know where it - it was on this pocket. And what he did, he locked her up in a room there, he went home to dinner, locked this girl up and she were - looking through the window and I never was mad in me life as at that girl, I'd got no interest in the g
irl at all, but I never was mad in me life at looking at that girl there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You were upset because of what the teacher had done?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What he - what he'd done to that - to that girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You thought it was very cruel?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - I never - I thought it were rotten.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did they emphasise was important when you were at school - did they say good manners were important?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - no, I don't - I don't think they - they ever bothered that way. They did here you know. They did -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 At school they didn't teach you anything was important?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No. Just the sums and the - well the - what they call it - the other things in the school. That were all they bothered about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The lessons you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. The lessons.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you have any regrets about your education?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Well I'll tell you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13108170\charrsid12525446 one}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  thing. At one time this schoolmaster he started giving points. And - if you get so many you had half a day - off school. O
nce in't week. Well there were two lads beside me - he stopped it. The two lads beside me would get this half day two weeks on running. And then as far as me mind runs it drops. So after that I'd - I'd no - not much interest in it. And I can remember anot
her time. You see, you worked - they weren't same as this fellow who's here, O'Neill, leading you and - and helping you. They - same as you - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 16}}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 0}}}four o'clock{\*\xmlclose} were - forgotten. That's what I have against the teachers today. It can be a hard job and it can be a 
damned easy one. O'Neill used to say, here, he used to say teaching were money for old rope.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This was when you were a boy was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. When I were a man here, when I were looking after school.
