\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Your dad hadn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. Nor I hadn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why didn't your dad have much use for Labour?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well - I don't know so much about him but I - I've got my own views. You see, I - I've been on the council, I did twelve years on council as an Independent. I don't think he did. 
We did discuss things, he'd talk politics at - at table, round table you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did he tell you why he liked being a Conservative?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't know. I can't really - I can't - go that far.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did he always vote?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, he always voted. And so do I, and I vote at council elections and I don't like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Before 1918 some men felt they risked losing their job if they didn't vote he way their employers told them to vote, did this ever happen to your father?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No. But - me dad - me dad told me about - there were some - some of the candidates for Parliamentary honours used to have gangs and they used to make people vote.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How do you mean they'd have gangs?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - just what you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 talking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What would the gangs do?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They just made - see that these people voted for their - their man. I can - I can remember - remember them telling me that.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You mean they'd make them vote by force?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - they - they - I don't suppose there'd be any bother but - they helped them along. I can just remember that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You don't mean just workers?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. I'll tell you another thing I remember. About - about voting.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This is when you were a boy was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes, when I - I - when I - oh I'd be - be - or when I'm working then. I don't know. But anyway there were - they were talking about a strike at paper mill. And this actually happened. A fellow as I knew were a car
etaker at top and - his boss, boss of works went to him and said - just go up yonder and come back and tell me who'd bobbing out at - these houses they had for the - for the ballot papers or something, and he says, and tell me yon two is making a cross an
d }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 making}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  their - selves busy. It got - it collected and got home them two got sacked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Because he found out who they were voting for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Because they were - they were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Helping a candidate?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, they were doing a - they're doing a bit too much. They got sacked and then }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 they}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 got took on again about twelve months after. I could have put them two on for that what for that money as - that - as they call - you can get - you get paid for it. There was a word for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your father ever help candidates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. No. No. No. Did nothing only bellowed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When he wasn't doing his work how did he spend his time, you say he bowled all the time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He used to make these pegs for measuring things out of bone. In't kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Tell me about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - I - I believe there's a pair in here you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Down in the mines they put a tin check on - what's this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well they put it through a hole in a - in a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 piece}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  of wood and - and it hangs down outside and when it goes up they knew where it is. Used to call it his you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 they put it on the wagons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, put it on the wagon. Well he used to make them checks for - a tin smith down at village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You said he used to get a shin bone?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Aye, used get a shin bone and used file it down in - in the fire at kitchen and make a flat plate for wrapping it round and he used make pegs at end for measuring with you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What would you measure with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well bowls - how far off they were off one another. When they're bowling you know. Give the men when they've finished bowling, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did he make the tags for down the pit - what did he make those of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He - oh well, the - the tin smith had have tin.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And your dad used to make them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, he used to go working for him at night. He wanted get in tin smiths shop but he got told for it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He didn't want to do it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, getting too old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How many evenings a week did your dad stop in when you were children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - I reckon - I think - well we used to go up bowling green you know, I mean, and watch 'em bowl. 'Til we g
ot bowling ourselves.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did he go a lot to the {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}bowling green{\*\xmlclose}
{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, everybody went up there at night you know. More or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What about in winter when there was no bowling, how often would your dad stay in with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh he - he had - he never did above two pints.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He used to go to a pub did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, he didn't get - he didn't get much drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How many evenings would he stay in the house with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh well we were little I don't think - I don't think he went out much 'til we'd gone bed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Then he would go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. Get about two then - 'course he were up at six. He were home at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname time}
{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Hour}{\xmlattrvalue 17}}{\xmlattr\xmlattrns0{\xmlattrname Minute}{\xmlattrvalue 30}}}half past five{\*\xmlclose} to start at six at pit you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So he'd wait until you went to bed then he'd go out?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That's it, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did he ever belong to a savings club or a boot club or a sick club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye - there was - there - the one at work. Of course there'd be no names mentioned and - I'd just got five quid in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This is before 1918 wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes, before that time. And the fellow comes down and I fancy were going to my brothers, he wanted borrow five pounds and he - he - he'd a kiddy as were lame and then - 
instead of going to me brother he come to me. Well he tell - pitches this yarn about this child you know. I said, well, I said, I say, I see if I can borrow it off missus. Her wouldn't have any. Anyway I went and drew it out of club.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Which club were you in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 At mill.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Used to have a club at the mill?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. And he's still owing it me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What sort of a club was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh - you could put what you liked in, some of them used to have as much as f
ifty or sixty quid, they'd put a quid a week in like that you know. Anyhow I - I never saved any after that lot.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your dad ever join a club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, no. No. He just spent it - his wage on us.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you ever remember a funeral in the family?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I can remember that time - I can remember that - that youngster as died. Of the girls. Yes. Walk in it. We walked it. Father and me and - and the girl and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did they take the baby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 In the - they carried it in a coffin. Oh they didn't - they didn't - didn't ride then. They were too poor.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What happened when they got to the cemetery then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - I - I mean the - the - they put - I - I just don't remember about it going in the
 grave but I went to funeral. Probably dad or somebody else carried it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What happened when you came back home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh just went - just normal.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You don't remember an adult funeral when you were a very young boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes, I can remember me grandfather up there, used to have a - a good do after. Used to have ham and - and - and corned beef and like of that you know. We had a good - a good do at a funeral.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What kind of clothes did they wear to go to the funeral?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 All wore black and black boots - ah. They wore black.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember anything else about a funeral before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, it - it - there were everyone alike. 'Course they were having - were having carriages and hearse
 then you know. It'd be a costly job in - cost's seventy or eighty quid bury anybody today.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You don't remember anything else about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, I can remember one - I can remember me dad died.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This was after 1918 wasn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. He were - he - he - no, I'm telling you and I - I'm right serious now, I know as I will.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That you'll rise again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. And I've no fear of dying. I - I don't 'cos of - I'm telling you now, the - the - there's I'm 
talking here talking this you know but I don't care if I die tonight as long as I've no pain. I'd be then about - nine years old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This coal mine was the top of the brew?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The - the - it were just at bottom of the brew - this brew you've come down now. And I used to go there - and you}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446  could}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  get a truck - they charge you halfpenny for a truck and the co}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 a}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 l was fivepence ha'penny so that was sixpence a - that - ha'penny make sixpence hundredweight and I used fetch it for people in the vi
llage. Generally Saturday morning when we're away from school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So you'd a part time job doing this?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well it wasn't a part time be job, I didn't get above penny or - or tuppence when I fetch somebody a hundredweight of coal you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That would want some pulling wouldn't it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well I - I mean that did. I used to get a hundred weight of coal and then put a hundredweight on top in a bag. Two of us, and get - probably get tuppence for fetching it. That went on with most of the lads.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you get spends for your parents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I get -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 As a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I never - you might a get an odd penny or tuppence but never more. He hadn't it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What happened on your birthdays as a child, did you have a party and did you get a present?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We never bothered about birthdays. But I - I don't yet. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was Christmas any different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh, Christmas, we used to have a bit of a dust up then we'd probably - w
e'd probably run to a piece of pork and as we get older it went - of course it went to turkey.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you get presents and did you do anything special with your father?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, somebody - yes, the fellow that we used to - as owned the ho
uses where we lived he used to give us a bit - say something about a - all }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 kids}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 a tanner each. And it - and it used to run to - well, you could get a {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname City}}Jaffa{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}
 then for a penny and - and we used to have to spend it at the end shop at the row.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Your home was rented was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever see anything of your landlord and what did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh he were all right were landlord.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He was good was he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh he - roughly we - the rent'd only be about three bob a week or something like that, if it were that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And he treated you O.K.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Aye, he used to give us a tanner out of it all the kids in the row. That were facing the chapel. And the chapel's pulled down now you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You lived at church View and then you moved to {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}
Market Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, number - {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname address}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname Street}}
hundred and eleven Market Street{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose}. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 Straight}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  facing the chapel.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why did you move to there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well anyway our aunt lived in
 the same row. And she said could like - she'd do something towards us as well as she could you know, her and me father and that girl.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She did something to help in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have a lot of relatives living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, had - the - father had - another brother. And he had a brother killed. The only one in }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 the pit}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  that was - well he were drowned. The river broke in at to - at a place down at Wringley.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Into the pit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And 
- yes - and the - the people that he worked with were coming out and they sent him back for the tools but he never came out. And he the only one }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 drowned}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 .
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But you had relatives apart from that living nearby?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, we'd some -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you see a lot of them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh yes, we were - the uncle Squire, me uncle Jim, my uncle Tom and - uncle Bill and they all lived in the village barring one and he lived up at - he lived up in North somewhere.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have a lot to do with each other as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Not a lot. Because - the eldest brother left at somewhere where the dye}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 works is now, some houses belonging to they and - they were a bit - bit religious }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 people}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and - no, not - none of the rest of the family were re - they didn't go to church, I'll not say they }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8792855\charrsid12525446 wasn\rquote t}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  religious but they didn't go to church. And he - he - well he built the pulpit and his son used to play the organ.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did anybody in your family make music, did you have musical instruments in your house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, we hadn't but this particular party that I'm talking about, one of them, his son was a brilliant violinist and the other brother played the French Horn and they were both in a orchestra together and - he went away and
 they came back and they both went to the same syrums they call them, playing there in an orchestra and both had a - a very good pension when they came out of it. And one of them had been in the Navy and - with the - with the orchestra.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever make music at home as a family - did anybody sing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes, I - I mean, beside that the father played in the - what they call then - Volunteer Bank. The Volunteers came and they called - and - and - and he - he'd go and look to the band sometimes. That were that side, that brother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 In your family did you ever make music?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Father didn't but - son used play violin a bit. And then - I used to sing to him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you had friends, you said your father used to bring his bowling friends home, how did they spend the evening then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He - he - he never fetched any of them people in. No, he - he - the girl did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your dad never have friends in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Very, very rare.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, he were - he - he were rather - he were rather older than shall a say - the rest of the people, I mean he - although he's a very - I told you he's a very good bowler he never brought - fetched any of them friends home and I've seen hi
m with three - three - two or three copper kettles hung on the roof.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where they used to give for winning these bowling handicaps.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why did he put them on the roof?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I mean there were no one else put them, not on the - they had no cupboards them days and they were just hung up on a -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You mean on the ceiling in the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Yes. I think, no, I've seen him with two hung up at once. He - as a bowler - he - he played a fel
ler on this - well, it's - it's not played on now but it's still going, agen the Grapes yon. It was open every night, you know, that's where they spent all their time, the people in the village. They used to come there as when there'd be any - finished at
 
pit and washed and then they used to go bowling there, and odd half crown or like of that. And I should think me dad was about best bowler as ever went down that green. I'll tell you why. He played - he played one fellow from Kearsley moor, he played him 
three times on that green and licked him three times but he never would go up and play him on his own green up on Kearsley Moor.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 'Cos he thought the fellow'd lick him if he went there. And you see -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He didn't want to be beaten?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
And this man - he won second, you know these sweepstake, well they were a big thing then, when they bowled at Blackpool, big bowling sweep there. That fellow as he licked three times - come second in one of them so he must have b
een a fairly decent bowler.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Tell me about the people generally in the village, can you tell me who was considered the most important person in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I should think the Fletchers family that owned the - that owned the mill down there the most - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 biggest}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  people in the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They were considered important because of this were they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I mean they owned the works you see. And - the - the - the people that didn't work in the pit then they generall
y worked at Fletchers you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you see the society in those days, they say that people divi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 d}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 e society into different classes or groups in that time before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I - I'll just tell thee something. I - I lived straig
ht opposite the chapel and - and it had a big burden on me for years.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well I'm just going to tell you why. If I'm stood on the doorstep I used stand - stand on the doorstep when they're coming out or - when they're going in and watch them. Well the chap comes down and he - he - well shall we say cadging. And this -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Who was cadging?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This - this fellow. He was a cadger and - you would - you would, you'll pick it up when you see what happens. And he - he e
yed all these people coming out of - out of chapel, he didn't get a penny piece. Now, about - half an hour after I'd just started }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 drinking}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  beer. I goes in the pub a bit lower down on the same side as where I lived. And - 'course I had a pint and a gill, so
mething like that, and this feller comes in, this cadger. And he - he goes around - he goes round and they all - some of them give him a penny, give him some - and one fellow paid for him a pint. So I've straight away begun weighing up the people in the p
ub and the people coming out of chapel. And to my - and it's lasted me as long as I've lived. The people who should have given him did not and the - well the - the people in the pub did. And it lasted }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 me all}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  me - it's lasted me all me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was he a very poor person or something?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well - he must be when he - when he - when he were begging of the people coming out of chapel and then he went in the pub and he pitched the yarn there and he got money and he got a pint.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Which class would you say you belonged to as a boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh I should say down amongst working classes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What sort of people belonged to the working class?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, they were - I said the bulk of the people were working class people. T
here wasn't any - any big fellows in the village at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What do you mean by big fellows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I - I mean, they - they - they were practically either colliers or working other people and one or two people as worked at Manchester.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember anyone you had to call sir or madam?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I don't think they ever did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No one at all in the village?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I only say I've been - chairman of the managers here at this school in the village here. Onl
y saw it happen there with the fellows used to own a factory up at - he }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 wound}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 the factory op on Kearsley Moor. And before he came down, when he - when he was the manager with a queer customer here -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was this before 1918?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I just thi
nk it were. Morning Sir. Ah. And when this fellow come here he stopped it. He went mad did this fellow. He was on the council when I was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did some people think themselves superior to other people and do you remember a distinction between craftsmen and labourers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I - I re - I should have thought - I don't think - I found it in the church here, I used to go to the church here, used to be in the choir but I used to see the Methodists, some of the top men of the Methodists used to think
 they were a little bit better than the other people.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But this was all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Some families were thought of as rough and some as respectable, do you remember this. You were telling me about a girl at school and you said she was dragged up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you mean by that - was she from a rough family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, I mean there weren't a - there wasn't a lot of money going in the house them days you know and this were a second wife to this girl and she downed herself and her - and her youngster beside in the - in the canal just across here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Because of the conditions at home. This second wife used to go up put a white sheet over her - over her head and frightened 'em at night time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I don't know. One day when the funeral was of that girl - them two girls - there were - the people used to come out and throw tin cans at back of them of the funeral process - wherever they were - they were remembered her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Suppose someone did something that everyone in the village disapproved of?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well that were it - that were it, they knew these things but couldn't prove anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So they used to throw tin cans?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They're throwing tin cans at the - funeral procession when it went down Wringley.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you ever remember any other incident like this of people who did wrong being shown up in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. I - I - I used to go - first I started drin
king beer, I never got any in the village, I used to go to a pub on the canal - the canal side yonder. And - one Sunday, I wasn't }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 then, we were going up there and a fellow used to go in that pub, they called him - then they called him Jimmy Up Back, this fellow. No, not Up Back, he was called - they called him {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}{\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname 
City}}Cork{\*\xmlclose}{\*\xmlclose} for something rather and he used to wear a pair of these cord trousers. And he were dying. We knew this, with going in the pub with him. And he had a son as used to go in there. And - the
re's another little pub close to, it's pulled then, so we decided to have a - a walk after we come out of these first pub and go this way. So - this chap's son comes out. Wearing these - his dad's pants. He'd only one pair of pants, these corduroys and th
e
re'd been about four men in that pub having a drink or two and he comes out with these pants. So when these four women saw him with them pants on they run at him and they knocked him down and they - and the other men stood by and they watched them, they k
icked him in his ribs and one thing and another and we - we - we never bothered.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He'd borrowed his father's trousers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He'd - he'd took 'em.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And the old man was still alive?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He died. They didn't - I never seen anything like it in me life.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember any other things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes. I - I can only remember - there's a Friary - you'll have seen that - that - that pub across the river there, come by them houses. I can only remember when they w
ere putting the main sewer down, I were but a lad then. And there were a lot of Irish - Irish peo - navv}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 ie}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
s and them things, working then. And - they used to go in that - in - in that second pub up there. I used to go and have a - I just started a drinking and - I went one day and - oh there's a fith - a couple of fights every weekend. Navv}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 ies}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and the colliers.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 U - I don't know what they had against one another but they used to seat after they got - beer was stronger then you k
now than it is now, it were only tuppence a pint. And they used to get quarrelling and - and - and there'd be a - a couple of fights every weekend there, the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 navvies}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and the colliers. I went in one day and they were singing and - I listens to this song and
 it were - the chorus, it used come out like this - no Irish need apply, or something like that and that were finishing up with the chorus and I can remember in the place used sing it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They didn't like the Irish?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. I've nothing a
gen the Irish but I - I mean, that what were they were singing with these Irish men in and they - the British if you like. And I said to me uncle Jim, I said, what's up, I said, is everybody singing this chorus. He says, can't you see it. No Irish need ap
ply, you know, for jobs. And there they were - they made a bother of it and it used to be sung every - every weekend.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you think the Irish were stopped from getting jobs though in the North here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh you've start a big - you start 
a - a big question when you start talking about that. I - down here there's a place called - Chloride, very big place and there's a few - there's a thousand or two works there. Ah well, come summer time and I remember - chaps coming to me in the club - in
 
this club here and they're telling me about their complaints about - about the Irish getting jobs for - and - and a fellow called - what were his name - Redmond, and they said - and I says - I said, what do you expect me to do about it? I said, I'm only a
 councilor, I said, and I - I couldn't bring a thing like that there. He wanted - at - at that time there's a - a feast in Bolton -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was this before 1918?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, it would be. And - there were a lot of unrest in country then, on jobs w
ithout gates. If a chap was an Irishman and went down to Chloride he could get on. Three people approached me in't club and tell me about this. Well, I said, I said, I don't know what you're telling me for but I said I can't do anything about it. Well I h
eard about this Redmond.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You went to Bolton Market and you heard a man talking about the Sinn Feinians?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well I mean the Sinn Feinians were all right with him you know but - the other people were - were - were his - cup of tea. Well anyway I comes back out at }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 Farnsworth}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and I - and - just when we were - few people - few soldiers killed in - in - if you recollect in Ireland.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This was before 1918 - before the end of the war?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, was the first war. I comes back 
out on it and - the very mob that I'm being with out there do you know, four soldiers killed out of that mob, in Ireland. And I thinks to myself, well that looks bad, these lads have been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 
fighting,}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  they come here to Ireland supposedly a peaceful country an
d they get killed. So I said, look here, I say, it's no use, I say, you're - you're talking to me but we were better friends after. Friend of - friend of mine was a Catholic, friend of one or two more were Catholics and they were pushing for jobs and bein
g
 pushed from church. So - I - I tell a question to this fellow and I says, I told him about these things. And he didn't deny them because he knew they were true. Anyway after the row we were friends again but - he never bothered me and I'll tell you I was
 with him in Blackpool.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 As a child do you ever remember any prejudice against the Catholics?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh no. No. But what made me get against them was here, you see, I used to work amongst them at the mill and - if any of them were Catholics
, I found out they were Catholic I used to talk, I used to talk in mill to lads and I used to be surprised at the amount of knowledge they had of what the English done at the Roman Catholics. You know, they couldn't have been above nine or twelve year old
. And how this were coming from them it come from the priest you see. But they never told them about the Spanish Inquisition and them kind of things - the other side of it. They knew nothing about that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember anyone in Farn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 worth being described as a real lady or a real gentleman and do you know why it was?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I can't - I can't say there w}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 ere}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  any outstanding personalities apart from the Fletchers. Barring this schoolmaster here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you see much of the police when you were a child and what did you think of him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I think - I think you did, I think you did, yes. Not very much. He used to say - that he - he - he could hang his - he could hang his watch - watch chain on a lamp-post somewhere about Grapes
 and nobody in the village dare - would take it. And he - he - and he run me uncle in about twice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - he's as nice a chap as - me uncle - as ever worked and he used to running a - well, walk straight there, walk strai
ght there, you know and then the police says - look at him standing there, and let him have one. Once tripped - threw his cape in brook, bottom of mill you. He did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Your uncle threw the policeman's cape in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Uh-huh.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What for?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Because he didn't like him and - and didn't like -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did he treat you children?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
He - he had no children. Oh he's comic. He used to think he were king of village I remember when we were going - when - well our 
- wasn't going school - I were going school and we used to sit in the window bottom of the end shop at row. He used to come and order us off. And - we used to give him cheek back and - he were at it one day and he says - he locked - he locked - he got me 
brother fined. There was a - there was a lady, I don't think this'll do for that anyway. And he had a goose under his arm.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was coming down Stoneclough Road?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah. Down Stoneclough Brew and he - he kept pulling at this goose's head.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The policeman did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, Albert did when they saw as he comes round. So he says - what'd you doing. He did it again and he pulled it again you know and they started fighting. Now policeman }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 comes up}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and he takes our Albert's name. Not t
he other fellow, he couldn't catch the other fellow. He issues a summons and Albert had to go to court and when he went to court he tell - tell them this yarn about what Albert had done and one thing and another about fighting. So, they asked our Albert i
f he'd any questions asked. He said, yes, he said, you've been fighting, he said, where's the other fellow. So magistrate said there were a mistake in summons and they altered it and they fined him about seven and a tanner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How do you think this policeman treated people though as a whole?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh if he - he - if he could get - well I tell you about he used to do me uncle Dick, he had him fined him twice. Our Albert, the next time he were done and quieter lad never walked than me - me brot
her, wouldn't - wouldn't bother. He - there were a woman sick again black Horse and - she were laughing and scoffing and I don't know whether Albert said anything or not but - that'll do you folks. He booked him again and another seven and a tanner.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you were young do you remember whether you you're your father had a hard job to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, he - he -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you feel about it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I'll tell you one thing and it - it - and I - I - I - he used
 to work at night, he used to work his turn at nights and I comes downstairs one morning -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How do you mean he worked his turn at night?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He worked at nights. He worked in at nights as I comes down and I sees him with - a round of br
ead in a basin and - some pepper and salt. Ten he went bed on't that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was he ever out of work and did he ever have to go anywhere for help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The only - only when there were strikes on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What happened then - how did you manage to live?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well I mean I told you about then going to - aye, soup kitchens and then these uncles were a bit better off, used to bring us a cow's heart or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You never had to go anywhere else for help?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You didn't have much poverty in the village at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, because - it was - the big colliery up on the top there. Thetwood Colliery.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That always kept people in work did it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Uh-hum.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember if your mother worked before she was }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and what she did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
That's where little - I know very little about me mother. I can only remember - only thinking about her this morning - sending me to school with schoolmaster. And that - a rose has been burnt - burnt down there. I'd be - be six or seven years old.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember where she came from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, she came out of the village.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where did your dad come from?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - he came out of the village but whether he - originally they came from Crewe}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 . The - the father, I}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 , talking about his father now, and he must have brought his sons with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you were young did you have a temperance club at your chapel and did you ever sign the pledge or anything?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, used to sign the pledge yes. Every other week.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why every other week?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - Wesleyans - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 Wesleyans}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  have one and then this other place that's pulled down, they'd have one. I don't - I don't remember ever having any at church.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You signed both of them did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh you si}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 gne}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 d every time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What happened at the temperance club?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well used to be one or two people out of the village sing and - used be -
 used to be - a playtime for lads. I remember one of the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 superintendents}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  of the place, he had a }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 bald}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 head, very bald head and one of the lads he would sit there messing with it like this, he messing with it - on the top - he didn't touch his head. Over top
, like he was talking. And another lad at this side could - knocked his head down. They took no notice.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What actually happened when you signed the pledge?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I mean - I don't think it made any difference but - I must have signed it half a dozen times more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was it just a matter of signing a form?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes. Just a form, a printed form and - ask why you signed to and one thing and another, I must have signed it half a dozen times.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Then broken it just as many times you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - I were - I were no age then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They made you sign very young did they?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, I - you used to go in - they'd get you going when you were six or seven years old you know and sing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You told me you started part time work at ten, what age did you actually finish school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I don't know much about finishing school, I went full time year after you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 At about eleven?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You just started part time first?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 For while - whole - while the half time period were on. And I went - I went at morning. And school at afternoon.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Then about eleven you went to full time work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Went full time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Can you tell me as a child who did you play with, did you play with your brothers or with neighbours?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 I played with me neighbours' friends, I tell you most of the - most of the playing were football at back.}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you play with anyone you pleased or did your father ever stop you from playing with certain children?;
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh no, me dad never bothered. Me father were very broad minded.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have any hobbies when you were at school, did you keep any pets or do gardening?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Aye, that's just what I missed. Well you see, I missed me mother you see and - and - and father were that fed up when he come home off work - come for work 'til - he didn't bother. Chap next door - we were friendly with, he went nigh
t school. He took shorthand, well I don't know anything about typing but he took shorthand then that - he - he - I - I had some hazy ideas about taking that up, it'd been best thing in me life I ever done if I took it up. Because if I - I always felt lack
 of it, even on council.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you go fishing or bicycling or play any sports?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I - the bulk of it were football.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever go to theatres in those days.?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, I go theatres. Oh that were - aye -
 that were the - they had a - the theatres still going up there, we used to - Morton Powells things and used to have Shakespeare, opera - oh yes. Used to attend them, I were very fond of opera you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Even as a child?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And - what 
is it - varieties used to come, used to go Bram at them time at Bolton. I seen all - all the big turns as come Bolton.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you left school did you still stay at home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh yes, I - I - I wouldn't have left 'til I were twenty-four year old 'til I get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you spend your Saturday and Sunday then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was it any different once you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I don't think I - I don't think it were any different.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you still go to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do I still go? Oh no, no, I - what happened - aunt come and brought me a new suit and I went church and went in't choir.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This was when you first started work was it?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. And then - then I - then we - then were getting a bit of money at house I could buy me - we could buy our own.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
What did you buy with your money and where did you go when you first started work, did you start doing different things then, did you start going out in the evenings?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 And}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 well I - I - I tipped up everything I had to me dad more or less.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you spend your spare time once you left school, when you first left school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Still playing football. Aye, and - and - youngest brother were a very good footballer.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you not make new friends, boys or girls, then after you started work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. I used to go - we used to go up }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 Farnsworth}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  but - I had an idea started dancing. I did - I - I went and - I met the lady of
 the dancing hall outside at - outside of street. All the others went dancing only me and another fellow. And - she started talking to me, said, if you'll come in her says, I'll teach you to dance. I said, aye, I said, but, I said, I still keep listening 
to these other lads. I said, they kept telling me about different girls in there and I said - I don't like it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you shy of girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't think I were. Only the tales they used to tell me about 'em - they - filled me up and I couldn't stand it and -

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Tell me about the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
She says, she said she'd teach me. I said, thanks, but I'm not going in. after I told her what I thought about it she said, well, she said, she says, you'll not miss much. And her husband were -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have to tell your dad where you were when you were working, and did you have to be in at a certain time?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, father never bothered me. Never bothered any of us. Only when I had to get - when - when youngest get }{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 . He started grumbling then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why they must have thought he were too young. I told him, I said let him alone.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You were twenty-four when you got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Twenty-four.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have to save up to get }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Save up? I got - I got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  - I had about - sixteen quid I think. And she'd a - she'd a bicycle and she sold it and got about fifty bob for it and I got a quid off me father and we got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 .
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where did you go to live?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Here. Yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And you've lived here ever since?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Been here ever since.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have a big wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Hadn't a big wedding. I come here - so - it was a Wednesday
, had a day off and I went to work the day after. And - I - I give here these sixteen pound and got a credit for that.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That sideboard?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And some other things that are getting worn out. And we got }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and we never we never had any - much bother.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you not have a big wedding or a lot of guests?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, there weren't any, only me and me brother and - and - the lady that stood.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Was it a chapel wedding?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you go on about housekeeping in those days?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well - I - I don't know about me giving her packet - I may - whether I give her packet on not but I never - I never left her short of money. I'm, just going to tell you something now this mustn't go on. She 
was very thrifty and I used to give her the money and mind you this girl, I'm telling you truth now, this girl as I went with, she was witness in our - she was a witness in a divorce case with another one of her pal. He divorced her. It cost him a hundred
 quid and he didn't give me anything, had me own expenses. Told this girl about this and I hadn't been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 above a - a couple of weeks. They did me tales about this youngster. My - my, mind you, I only went one night with this lady and I - I question today whether - whether it could have been hung on me or not.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you did start up housekeeping how did you change things from your own childhood?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I didn't change anything, I left everything - I trusted her. I always did and I did t
oday for that matter. This - this thing here, this were first - this were - in an Ideals Home, the first prize.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you any different from your dad, did you help your wife about the house?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, I used to turn the squeezers and - and like of that. And help her wash kiddies at -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And put them to bed did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - well she put them to bed, I used to delight in washing kids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You liked that did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. We hadn't the bath then, we'd one of first baths in village and we were the first electric house in village. Yes.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How many rooms have you got here, is it four?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Three upstairs. It should have been - it should have been - made into like there now brought up to date anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 did you live on your own or did you have any relatives living with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We had no relatives with us and in the - in the - in the - we had a big tub for washing the kids in. I - I used to get in w
ith the little one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you read stories to them and that sort of thing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 More, I used to play with them and - but - the kids themselves they'd - they've had everything like - like having these }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 encyclopedia}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  and - and - all the books I could - lay me hand on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You liked them to read a lot did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes. It's been their fault as their not gone - well they've all done very well but I mean - they did start going to a school but they - the two eldest chucked it. You
 see, while I were in the Army were a bit pinched for money. Then - things might have been different but for that - that - eleven months.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you strict with your children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. I never - I - I never - I never beat one only - only
 the son. And that were through the neighbours. He's a bit obstinate today but he'd all right. He - I found him in at back of the alley coming up to Kearsley here and he were run with a fellow called Tony Tuffus, he were a - a billiard player and he used 
to drive this car like mad - like for mill there. And I watched him and he stands again the that house there, house across there, and when he - he's watching this car - car come round, when it turns corner he runs out and grabs back and he's }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 swinging}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  away. 
I think to myself, there's something in what these women keep saying about this lad. I'll paste him. Anyway I stripped him and took him upstairs and pasted him and when he come down to the - I could have - I could have cried for him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 It upset you more them him?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. Coming back - coming from work day after it'd be no }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1997397\charrsid12525446 
danger}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  from seeing him swinging from back just the same.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You never laid a hand on any of them again?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. That was only time I ever whacked him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your wife do all her own washing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes. She used to do the washing in house. I used to sit where you sit there put them - heaters in the fire and fish them out and put them in, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The irons?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. Used to help the women ironing.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did your wife cook, did she have a range or did she have gas?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh we got a - we used to have - used to cook on there at the beginning then we got to - a gas stove.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did she make the children's clothes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She did. The children - sewed the children's clothes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you do any cobbling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I used to do cobbling and then I chucked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Because I - I - I found it out that - I - I were getting money enough.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did the children have to help in the house at all?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - I can't - I can't say as they did very much, she was all doing, Mrs Fox.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 A very busy women?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I should think she were. She were 
- she wasn't - make - well liked with the rest of the women in here I mean she'd a way of her own. Exceptionally clean. She - she bought this, I had nothing do with it and this, I - I wouldn't know where this come from, this and - she - I never queried an
ything about these things, she bought these things. Isle of Man. From the time of her - a day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She used to go to the Isle of Man for a day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, and - we went, it must have been forty times and - the - she used to charge us seven an
d six. I'll never forget being in one time and we were talking, we were talking about Earl Kane, some people here, people in there people with money more or less apart from our tribe. So they started talking about Earl Kane so I chipped in I said, I said,
 
Earl Kane's not much of a writer. Why with that one woman - one woman flew up. I said, well, I said, before he started writing, I said, he used to review books for a newspaper, I said, and lots of the things he's used in his books is what he's read. So I 
said, anything I -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you first lived in this house where did you eat your meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We used to have a table here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 In the front here?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And you wife cooked in the back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
, were you all able to have breakfast together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Used to get up - used to get up as six o'clock you know and - I - I'd get - she used to send me breakfast. No, she didn't send me breakfast but I come home for me dinner.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Used to take your breakfast with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did the eating change, what did you have now when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  for breakfast?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh we used to have bacon and egg of a morning or -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Every day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I - I didn't care what I got me breakfast but I wanted a good dinner and a good tea when I came home.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What would you call a good dinner and a good tea?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I mean - I used to find - I used to find do - the work t
hat I did - potatoes didn't do - didn't do for me so we used to have it at tea. We used to have a potato pie or - or - stewed beef and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 c}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ow}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 heel or something like that with a - always with a suet crust on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What about Sundays n}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 o}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 w }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 you}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Sunday we used to have a - invariable leg of lamb. It - it'd just go round you know with - five of them and missus and me.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you came home for your lunch what would you have then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 At supper?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you have at lunchtime?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That's what I'm talking about.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Potato pies?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, used to have it then. 'Cos I - I - I used want go to sleep when I'd potato pie dinner time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you have for teas then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well that's we had to - what you're talking about at - oh well we used to have boiled ham and - and corned beef and used some very good stuff then in mutton line in tins, I don't see it now.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your wife bake her own bread?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh bake, aye, used to bake - eight loaves. And we used to have a big tin at bottom of there with half a load of flour in.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did she make jam and pickles and things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Used to make jam, I carried - I carried - carried strawberries down and black currants up Farn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 worth, baskets and baskets. Had a big pan for making it. I used to stir it up while she were making it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You never grew your own vegetables when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Where did you grow them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I had 'em on back where them houses is. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever keep any livestock or pets?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Used to keep about - nearly a hundred hens on back there at one time.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You didn't have livestock as a child did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh no. Oh - used to have - pigeons and - and another fellow as I palled with used to have some room for all that and I remember - I remember him buying a dandy cock and a - and a hen and we used to have some - used to keep canaries, used t
o have a big breeding cage on the top so when father's gone out they put this - this cock and this hen on - up on the roof in - in kitchen. Aye. When it gets about two at morning this cock }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 
starts}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  crowing you know like. Father sticks up his head. That damn 
bird. I didn't hear him I got used to him. My father didn't get used to him and I can hear him swearing him now when - aye, pulled it - aye, pulled it down and put a - a towel - put a towel over it, keep it quiet 'til we got up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 But after you }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  
you said you kept about a hundred hens?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Back here.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You had an allotment then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Used to grow about - I used to grow tomatoes - tomatoes and - and chrysanths. I liked chrysanths.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever get any meat from poaching after you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes, just an - just an odd couple of rabbits now and again, couldn't get them so often. You used to get rabbits you know but - these as were freshly caught were much better than the others.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How about your children's table manners, what did you change there, were you very strict with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, they just did it, we never had any bother. Only with this - with the lad. He wouldn't want this and want t'other but - but he used to have same as the rest.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 He had to eat what he was given did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, he did - he's all right now, makes it - }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 tells me}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  what he's having you know before he goes out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you all have your own places at table?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They just sit - sit round there in't kitchen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you allow your children to leave the table when they wanted or did they have to ask?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I mean, we all practically finished at once.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Could they ask for a second helping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
You could have what there were going. They were never short of grub. Never had any - any trouble with them, only one. She's a tailoress. She's the only as is - is a bit - and that was through having porridge. She was allergic to it I m
ean, she was - she'd break out. When she finally stopped porridge she was all right. The others never bothered. They were all fetched up on porridge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you think there was a wrong and a right way to bring up children, what were your ideas of bringin
g up children? Did you and your wife talk about it together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No, I don't think we ever did and - and - they never - they didn't ever get any - they never put up for gaffers or anything like that, only this lad when he first started going school, he were a bit awkward. He was the only one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You never had any trouble with them?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you think was the correct way to bring up children, do you remember, had you any special }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 ideas}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  on it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - I can't say as I - say as I have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have a mother-in-law near?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Yes. Yes. Yes. She was all right. Aye, a good mother - I remembers her in me prayers every night yet. I liked her. And she was another woman as wouldn't - that wasn't liked.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I didn't - she didn't like rest of women but she liked men. I mean, not in a - a in a normal sort of way but she'd sooner talk to men than talk to women. Wouldn't have it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She wouldn't tittle-tattle with them you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh no. No, she'd talk - said she'd talk with the men.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Could your children come and talk to you and talk their worries over with you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, they could tell me anything they liked, they used to tal
k about anything - everything while they were there. Yes, I - I told you about having - having that' that book - what was it - I found it out as they were reading that. So I put it out of way.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You didn't want them to read that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, well they were - they were too young, but anyway the three of them had it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Can you tell me if there were any special things you felt you ought to do for your children like being affectionate or did you worry about the food or the discipline or their safety?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - the - the - I don't think they ever ned any. They never led - they never led - barring the lad.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you ever able to leave them and go out, you and your wife together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, we used to leave them and I used to - I left 'em one time and we were going Farn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
worth Market, me and the missus. We never went in pubs. And - me and another fellow were sitting here and we're carting Tetleys bitter from pub door opens. We'd had three or four jugs of this stuff
 - she comes in with two kids and stepped in that little room in their pyjamas. She starts blowing steam. I says, I've never been out. And I haven't been out. No, she were - and anyway I said, thou'll not come out anymore. I put to - two pieces of }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 chain in}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  on so they couldn't come down and get out. This short length and two nails, they couldn't get out that way.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 She thought you'd let the children out did she?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 Oh no}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
, she did, she didn't know what they were doing - she come on and followed them they were looking through shop window about ten o'clock at night and me and this fellow was sitting - oh, and when she came in she never said anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When grown-ups were talking did you let your children join in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes,
 they - they used to - used to go playing tennis at - Alice - the eldest was a very good tennis player. She used to go up there and the others used to go and it - and Alice were that good she wouldn't let the other sister play with her. Her come in wailin
g. Oh I couldn't make her play with her if she didn't want her - the one smaller - wouldn't let her play the - ball back with her. And they used to go to dances.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Could they play with anybody?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They could go out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Suppose another child hit them did you encourage them to hit back?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Hit back? I used let them fight, they used to come in I say, oh well go and fight it out. A }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15018283\charrsid12525446 woman}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  came with a kid here - her said, said, your Alice has been hitting her and so and so. W
ell I said, they fight - Mrs Fox says, well fetch her and let them fight it out here. Well said to her daughter, go on, right pull - pull Alice half top of her. That was how we used to treat them. If they fight they had to fight. We never - but the others
 used to come, now take this instance. This lad. When he were going school -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 This is your boy }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 you\rquote re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  talking about?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Yes. Going school I used to teach him how to - how to box. I said, look here, I said, whenever you start fighti
ng, I says, keep this here clenched. I said, don't let 'em get by this one and used to keep at him and - said, with this you know. It had some queer results. I used get fighting at school and was practice this you know and - used to be bringing them round
,
 so and so bit on - hit - getting hit on nose. Well I mean, he - you know. He were a good lad were this lad. That was the one - the wrong thing is - the only thing as I refused to teach him. He's a - he's a blessed good runner were this lad, he's as good 
as me dad were and I wouldn't follow him out. I think on and get - used to take him beer. Well -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you think runners always took beer?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well one - some of them did, professional runners and I wouldn't bother with him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you bring your children up to think was important in life, do you remember that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I used to teach 'em their prayers you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Do you remember anything special you though they ought to learn?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I used to - I ke
ep the lads in handling and I told her - I told her as she'd got to look after the girls. What she taught them I don't know. But I - I - I took this lad in handling. I put him as right as I could.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 So she was left to bring up the girls?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye, aye.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And you brought up the boys?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 That way, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When your children had a birthday was it any different you're your birthdays?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, I don't suppose it was only when they were twenty-one. I'd aunt, she bought Alice a gold watch.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did they never have parties, your children? Or presents?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, sometimes you used to bring girls to tea.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What about Christmas, was it a special day in your home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. The - 
the Boxing Day were because Alice were born on Boxing Day you see. She'd have been born on Christmas Day if I'd - if she'd have let me go for the midwife but - she wouldn't let me go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't know, she said it was nothing to what she'd go through - like the other women's tales.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And your wife wouldn't let you go for the midwife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, wouldn't let me go. Or she'd been born on Christmas Day, Alice would.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did you do on Christmas Day though as the children grew up, was it different to home?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well we used to - we used to have a - a turkey you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 And presents for the children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. We never bothered - presents. They do now, they - they all do.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did any of your children learn to play musical instruments or did any of them sing, did you make music together?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, they - they were never - any desire for that at all. Oh they could have done.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you play games with your children?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh we were always playing games, we used to play when we I - when they'd gone out or - I - there used to be the - about two in beside the - the rest of them so we used to play - follow me leader. And - I remember playing one time and - they 
were running and we run under table, upstairs under beds and over beds and we get playing, then I come - when I - I looks one of bedsteads leg were poking through there.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Through the ceiling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye, there were short boarding as I didn
't know about and it had - it had - it must have been nailed properly and instead of that it come sticking down. Well they. -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What did your wife say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh - when we were playing this game you know she - we used to have about an hour 
of it, I used to - wet my finger and then go - black my face and make them every one do the same, we used to have a -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why black your face?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - playing this game a hell of a time. Everyone had do what the other did you know. They used roll with laughter.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 It was a sort of follow my leader?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. Aye. What one did the other did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have a lot of books and newspapers when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes, I get - I get - well nearly all -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I mean when the children were little.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Aye. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 
Arthur Mead's books, children's Encyclopedia, I had the children's Bible yet.}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you take your children out a lot visiting neighbours and friends and did you take them out shopping?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Not - not so often. The - the - I used to take 'em out with - I don't think they're so very often with us only when went on holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You had holidays when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh we - we - when we got them o
n their feet. Aye. I tell you went forty times to Isle of Man. Used to love going there, I don't like it now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you go away on Bank holidays too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, just the - just the week - fort - week and fortnights holiday.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you ever take the children out just on your own?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh aye, used to take 'em walking of a Sunday. I went out one Sunday, I never forget, about Christmas time and we went - we went up - up to - I don't know the way now but it - it - it's through t
he fields up onto - it's a good long walk and then we used to finish up in Bolton and then come back along the canal bank. We had the dog with us then. Eeh I - I never forget that, there were no - there were nobody out only me and them four kids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You liked taking your children out then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh aye. I - I love kids today. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did your children go to Sunday school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 They went - every one went Sunday school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Were you still Wesleyan? Did they go to the Wesleyan?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, they went here. And - and - and this lad disliked going.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I don't know but lads like that disliked it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you and your wife go together to church?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Not so often. Just at sermons and one thing and another. I - I wasn't that - thought that a mistake.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I - I think if the parents go you can't expect the children go.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 If they don't go you can't expect the children to go you mean?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Mm, mm. I - I - I've come to that con - oh I - I - I don't think I've had - I've had anything ever different to - to life now but I can see the mistakes. I'll tell you about some -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Looking back what do you think were the mistakes you made?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Well - I'll tell you. When I was a spinner - there was seven - there were - sixty pair of mules there, that means sixty spinners. And when they - when you went in you'd everyone a pint a piece, you'd two cheques, you'd two fourpenny cheques, t
hat were two pints. You see? And - out of the six -
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When you went in the mill you had to?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Oh - I'm talking about going in place for meetings, after monthly meeting. There'd be I - there'd be - out of the sixty spinners there'd be at least fifty-four were either a pint or a gill. Only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 about}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
 four - four teetotallers and the rest of them used to come up for beer. I come to the idea that the only four in - in the place with any brains. Yes, were those didn't drink.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You didn't join the temperance club when you were older?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, no. No. No, they went out.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you say grace at meals when you were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2183843 Married}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 ?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Or family prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No. No. There's one - there's three of them does now.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Who taught your children to say their prayers?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Who told them what? Either me or - mother - mother didn't much, probably me. I'm teaching the grandson as comes here. Tell you - tell you truth, I'd still have the old times - hard as they were - than these.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Why?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well I think the food were better.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 What else?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Well - I mean, you - in other words you made your own - you made your own fun and then went pictures started, 'cos ye
ars ago there were pictures you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How do you mean you made your own fun, you mean when you were in the house together as a family?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 We used to play - dominoes and cards all four of us you know. Oh aye, every - every - they could all play them games.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you take an interest in politics, you were on the council and you were}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 
 independent}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12525446  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 I - I did not. I read politics but I - I were on the council. I care nothing about the councils you know. It's a lot of -
 I read the - I read the - the Farn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid603803\charrsid12525446 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
worth Journal about what happens and - and to me it's all bunkum. They build up you know, these people. They talk.
