\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 When the children were born who helped then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh - used to have an old lady come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 The midwife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 No, no, lady - lady come in give her a - give her a - give her five bob. And then I used - I }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15018283\charrsid12525446 used}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  to do when I come in.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you and your wife have a lot of friends who visited and you went out to see?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Ah friends - no, I mean we didn't have a lot of friends she'd one. Lived at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Bolton
{\*\xmlclose}, behind the brewers you know at {\*\xmlopen\xmlns2{\factoidname place}}Bolton{\*\xmlclose}. She - hers dead too. And I forget - forget that lot. She used to go there do a bit of cleaning while I were at Farn}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid15018283\charrsid12525446 s}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 worth. Oh most big place it were. And take two kids with her.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Did you have a hard time at any time to make ends meet?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
I don't think we ever did. I tipped it up you see, I give her the money. And then there were that ten bob I give that woman and that youngster died when he was about - about twelve months old or something like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Is there anything you would have changed in your marriage looking back? Tell me about the happy times and the sad times?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Oh I - I got - I don't suppose there's anything I would have changed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You enjoyed it did you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 Yes. Of course I enjoyed it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 How did you meet your wife?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
Damn funny. Ah. Well I'll tell you how I dropped on her. That fellow I told you about which was Irish. He's on top of a bus. And he had this - He had Mrs Fox
 with him. He said, he said, will see you home? So I said, I said, not going home. So - he said, we've been Lynch and other fellows he was singing and another, kept a big wine lodge and he said, have a drink or two. I - so we come home and we come down sl
o
pe here. So - I said look here, coming down road. I said to her, will I see you tomorrow? With having a drink or two - nothing would have happened you know, I wasn't that way. She said, yes. So - I said - I saw her. Went out a time or two. Then we went Bl
ackpool.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 For the day?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid12614909 FARNWORTH, LANCS  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 
No. Not for a day. It weren't - not that what they were. I said, we'll get we couldn't catch our train back, let's go and get some lodgings. So when I gets some lodgings her got one bedroom and I've got another about two away. }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid15018283\charrsid12525446 I says}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446  to her I says, you'll see me tonight. And I did.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16388725 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2122143\charrsid12525446 You know in a family has rows?
